  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Central Limit Theorem
Formula: Sample means → normal distribution
Note:    Foundation of statistical inference and polling

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Age of Universe
Formula: 13.8 billion years
Note:    Determined by CMB and Hubble constant measurement

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Euler's Identity
Formula: e^(iπ) + 1 = 0
Note:    Relates five fundamental constants; called most beautiful equation

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   E = mc²
Formula: E = mc²
Note:    Mass-energy equivalence; foundation of nuclear physics

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Boyle's Law
Formula: P₁V₁ = P₂V₂
Note:    Pressure and volume inversely proportional at constant T

============================================================
  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Diabetes Type 2
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Lifestyle
Symptoms:    Thirst, frequent urination, fatigue
Treatment:   Metformin, lifestyle, insulin
Deaths/yr:   1.5M
Vaccine:     No
Discovered:  1922

Disease:     Ebola
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Ebola virus
Transmission:Bodily fluids contact
Symptoms:    Fever, bleeding, organ failure
Treatment:   Monoclonal antibodies, supportive
Deaths/yr:   0.001M
Vaccine:     Yes (Ervebo for Zaire strain)
Discovered:  1976

Disease:     Hepatitis B
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HBV
Transmission:Blood, sexual contact
Symptoms:    Often asymptomatic; jaundice
Treatment:   Antivirals (tenofovir)
Deaths/yr:   0.82M
Vaccine:     Yes (highly effective)
Discovered:  1965

